snippet:
Por desgracia he tenido que ir varias veces con mi madre a urgencias.
Cuánto médico joven y que bueno es el trato, si hay mucha gente es obvio que hay que esperar, pero tratan al enfermo con una paciencia y una delicadeza que da gusto.
Siempre que hemos ido he salido con la misma sensación.
Felicidades a esos pedazo profesionales del servicio de urgencias
user.name: alicantina alicantina

extracted_snippet.translated:
Unfortunately I have had to go to the emergency room with my mother several times.
What a young doctor and how good the treatment is, if there are many people it is obvious that you have to wait, but they treat the patient with a patience and delicacy that is a pleasure.
Every time we have gone I have left with the same feeling.
Congratulations to those great professionals from the emergency service
